 ## Architecture[m
 [m
[32m+[m[32m### WebSocket[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m- Endpoint: `ws://localhost:3000/ws`[m
[32m+[m[32m- Auth: cookie-based (same as REST JWT)[m
[32m+[m[32m- Events: cultivation tick, chat messages, combat updates, notifications[m
[32m+[m[32m- Client: `socket.io-client` in `apps/web`[m
[32m+[m[32m- Server: `@nestjs/platform-socket.io` in `apps/api`[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m### BullMQ job queues[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mAPI uses Redis-backed BullMQ for async jobs:[m
[32m+[m[32m- `cultivation` — cultivation tick (every 30s)[m
[32m+[m[32m- `body-cultivation` — body cultivation tick[m
[32m+[m[32m- `liveops-cron` — weekly/daily cycle jobs[m
[32m+[m[32m- Other module-specific queues[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mWorkers run in-process with the NestJS app.[m
