[32m+[m[32m### Static catalog system[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mContent (items, skills, monsters, dungeons, missions, realms, bosses) lives in `packages/shared/src/*.ts` as static TypeScript — NOT in the database. This means:[m
[32m+[m[32m- No `prisma db seed` needed for catalog data[m
[32m+[m[32m- Frontend and backend share the same typed source[m
[32m+[m[32m- Adding content = editing TS files + building shared + running tests[m
[32m+[m[32m- DB only stores references (string keys) + runtime state (inventory qty, progress)[m
